{"tid":2402084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傑斯申請保釋被拒 案件押後至5月10日再聆訊","createTime":"2021-02-10T08:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T08:10:45.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"376a9d97e30ee0b4a4023897c2f5ae9ec3f35e67","tid":2402084,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"【速報：￼傑斯申請保釋被拒】<br />\n<br />\n著名網台主持人傑斯今日臨時提堂，被控國安法。辯方申請￼￼￼保釋失敗，案件押後至5月10日再聆訊￼。法官指辯方可向高等法院申請保釋。￼<br />\n<br />\n傑斯妻子亦有被捕，暫時保釋，不久前才完成手術。有一名21歲女兒，就讀港大最後一年。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：爆炸頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116178588425696/posts/3845194472190737/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116178588425696%2Fposts%2F3845194472190737%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=8604d121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116178588425696/posts/3845194472190737/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c147297c0b1653e92ce715985f4f6a88cebbab32","tid":2402084,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e867bab41ad17ebf375983488b83e9e3de0cf65","tid":2402084,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"又係蘇惠德"},{"pid":"d5c3b87a1ffe8d955e6bd07d9da8d559167e7b8b","tid":2402084,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"D100 網台主持人「傑斯」（原名尹耀昇）被指在節目引起他人憎恨、蔑視中港政府，被控 4 項「作出具煽動意圖的行為」罪。案件前日提堂，「傑斯」當時留院未有出庭，他今日（10 日）出院立即被帶到西九龍裁判法院應訊。「指定法官」、總裁判官蘇惠德聽畢控辯雙方陳詞，拒絕被告保釋，將案件押至 5 月 10 日再訊，以候警方調查與被告有關的片段、言論及財務資料。「傑斯」需要還押過年。「傑斯」女兒傷心不已，大叫「老豆」，旁聽人士亦著他撐住，「傑斯」則與他們揮手道別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3885522004866724/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3885522004866724%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=fbdae15d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3885522004866724/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b196ed5ffd0d01436dcb391b70be42ea9b0bf881","tid":2402084,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:06:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c12e427080524629a2d032745db3850369a100a","tid":2402084,"uid":184022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff345ab2231536b516cbce5ace9d53aac0f2e4d","tid":2402084,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"好撚陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeac1b7febb36bdb2b0b943f89d83bc472d2f348","tid":2402084,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605e1692021b7b57543f16225e33298e40f11290","tid":2402084,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"未審先坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴線"},{"pid":"db17222292cf6a14fee6813d2f072cc132a0f360","tid":2402084,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c65cfc339f36e18885ec72454e31ed2c9631c6","tid":2402084,"uid":4942,"li